      <title>中国人民银行暗示鸽派政策决心增强，流动性充裕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/pboc-signals-greater-resolve-on-dovish-policy-ample-liquidity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继出台旨在降低地方债务风险的大规模财政刺激计划后，中国央行加强了对支持性货币政策的决心，并承诺使用多种工具确保市场流动性充裕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/pboc-signals-greater-resolve-on-dovish-policy-ample-liquidity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 12:26:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
