      <title>西班牙灾难性洪水将使保险公司损失超过 38 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/spanish-flood-insurance-claims-to-top-3-5-billion-moody-s-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪估计，上个月底袭击西班牙瓦伦西亚地区的洪水预计将引发超过 35 亿欧元（38 亿美元）的保险损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/spanish-flood-insurance-claims-to-top-3-5-billion-moody-s-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 12:24:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德或将入股 Millennium</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/blackrock-may-take-stake-in-millennium</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，贝莱德公司正在与 Izzy Englander 的 Millennium Management 进行谈判，以收购其 700 亿美元对冲基金的少数股权。彭博社的 Manuel Baigorri 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/blackrock-may-take-stake-in-millennium</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 12:22:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
